# Result

Telegram mode is now present, operational, and documented with a safer configuration story:

* Telegram can be used as a real transport
* access remains restricted to one configured source
* traces and meta evaluation still run on every accepted message
* stdout remains the operator-facing observability channel
* live bot secrets are no longer meant to live in tracked JSON config
